      <h1>Linux for Advanced Users</h1>
      <p>These distros are more difficult to set up and are often run by experts who enjoy the challenge.  That said, they are not particularly difficult, and the communities that support the distros are always eager to help.  Gentoo - renowned as one of the most hardcore linux systems, also has the very best documentation.</p>
